data.description: Welcome to Lynn Haven! This Delray floor plan is one of the most desirable layouts in Andrews Plantation. Features include a four sided brick home, beautiful LVP flooring throughout, plush carpet in bedrooms, granite countertops, and 9' ceilings throughout. The kitchen is open with a center island and large corner pantry. Centrally located to shopping, dining, schools, with convenience to the Worlds Most Beautiful Beaches and Military Base(s). This home offers a large covered porch with a completely fenced yard space for privacy. With only one owner, this home has been well maintained and is move in ready. Call your realtor to view this beauty today!
